ust: No faith for one who cannot be trusted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn 'Urwah reported: 'Urwah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBe not deceived by the prayer of a man, nor by his fasting. Whoever wills can fast and whoever wills can pray, yet there is no religion for one who cannot be trusted.\u201d Source: al-\u012ama\u0304n li Ibn Abi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36794,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/08\/11\/simple-life-of-the-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":38317,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Zuhd: The simple living of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: She said to \u2018Urwah, \u201cO my nephew, we used to sight three crescent moons in two months without having any fire to cook in the house of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d \u2018Urwah said, \u201cHow did you live?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWith the two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25060,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/11\/urwah-torah-tawrat-hikmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38317,"position":3},"title":"&#8216;Urwah on Torah: Gentleness, mercy are head of wisdom","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Shaybah reported: 'Urwah, may Allah hav